# SEO Optimization — gokulk.vercel.app

## 1. OPTIMIZED `<head>` SECTION

For a **Next.js** project, add this to your `app/layout.tsx` (App Router) or `pages/_document.tsx` (Pages Router).

---

### Option A — Next.js App Router (`app/layout.tsx`)

```tsx
import type { Metadata } from "next";

export const metadata: Metadata = {
  metadataBase: new URL("https://gokulk.vercel.app"),
  title: "Gokul K — Full Stack Developer & AI Engineer | Tamil Nadu, India",
  description:
    "Gokul K is a Full Stack Web Developer and AI Engineer based in Tamil Nadu, India. Specializing in React, Next.js, Supabase, Firebase, and AI-powered web apps. View Gokul's portfolio, projects, and case studies.",
