## 2. JSON-LD STRUCTURED DATA (Person Schema)

Add this as a `<script>` tag just before `</body>`, or in Next.js as a component using `next/script`.

```html
<script type="application/ld+json">
{
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "Person",
  "name": "Gokul K",
  "alternateName": ["Gokul", "Gokulk"],
  "url": "https://gokulk.vercel.app",
  "image": "https://gokulk.vercel.app/og-image.png",
  "jobTitle": "Full Stack Developer",
  "description": "Gokul K is a Full Stack Web Developer and AI Engineer based in Tamil Nadu, India, specializing in React, Next.js, Supabase, Firebase, and AI-powered web applications.",
  "address": {
    "@type": "PostalAddress",
    "addressRegion": "Tamil Nadu",
    "addressCountry": "IN"
  },
  "email": "mailto:gokulk24cb@psnacet.edu.in",
  "knowsAbout": [
    "React",
    "Next.js",
    "Full Stack Development",
    "Artificial Intelligence",
    "Supabase",
    "Firebase",
    "Kotlin",
    "Android Development",
    "TypeScript",
    "Web Development"
  ],
  "sameAs": [
    "https://github.com/Gokul-k07",
    "https://www.linkedin.com/in/gokul-k-23334b329/"
  ]
}
</script>
```

### For Next.js App Router — create `app/components/JsonLd.tsx`:

```tsx
export default function JsonLd() {
  return (
    <script
      type="application/ld+json"
      dangerouslySetInnerHTML={{
        __html: JSON.stringify({
          "@context": "https://schema.org",
          "@type": "Person",
          name: "Gokul K",
          alternateName: ["Gokul", "Gokulk"],
          url: "https://gokulk.vercel.app",
          image: "https://gokulk.vercel.app/og-image.png",
          jobTitle: "Full Stack Developer",
          description:
            "Gokul K is a Full Stack Web Developer and AI Engineer based in Tamil Nadu, India, specializing in React, Next.js, Supabase, Firebase, and AI-powered web applications.",
          address: {
            "@type": "PostalAddress",
            addressRegion: "Tamil Nadu",
            addressCountry: "IN",
          },
          email: "mailto:gokulk24cb@psnacet.edu.in",
          knowsAbout: [
            "React",
            "Next.js",
            "Full Stack Development",
            "Artificial Intelligence",
            "Supabase",
            "Firebase",
            "Kotlin",
            "Android Development",
            "TypeScript",
            "Web Development",
          ],
          sameAs: [
            "https://github.com/Gokul-k07",
            "https://www.linkedin.com/in/gokul-k-23334b329/",
          ],
        }),
      }}
    />
  );
}
```

Then import it in `app/layout.tsx`:
```tsx
import JsonLd from "@/components/JsonLd";
// ...
<body>
  <JsonLd />
  {children}
</body>
```

