      </article>
    </section>

    <!-- AI SECTION -->
    <section id="ai" aria-labelledby="ai-heading">
      <h2 id="ai-heading">AI Systems by Gokul K</h2>
      <p>
        LLM features, document pipelines, and workflow automation that feel native—not bolted on.
        Clear boundaries, observability, and UX that earns trust.
      </p>
