      </p>

      <address>
        <strong>Gokul K</strong> — Full Stack Developer / AI Enthusiast<br />
        Tamil Nadu, India<br />
        <a href="mailto:gokulk24cb@psnacet.edu.in" aria-label="Email Gokul K">gokulk24cb@psnacet.edu.in</a><br />
        <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/gokul-k-23334b329/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" aria-label="Gokul K on LinkedIn">LinkedIn</a>
        <a href="https://github.com/Gokul-k07" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" aria-label="Gokul K on GitHub">GitHub</a>
