## 4. IMAGE ALT TEXT RULES

Every `<img>` tag must follow this pattern:

```html
<!-- Profile photo -->
<img src="/gokul-k-profile.jpg" alt="Gokul K — Full Stack Developer based in Tamil Nadu, India" width="400" height="400" loading="lazy" />

<!-- Project screenshots -->
<img src="/projects/nextstop-screenshot.png" alt="NEXTSTOP BusTracker project by Gokul K — real-time college bus tracking app" width="800" height="450" loading="lazy" />

<img src="/projects/ai-resume-screenshot.png" alt="AI Resume Maker and Analyzer built by Gokul K — AI-powered resume scoring app" width="800" height="450" loading="lazy" />

<img src="/projects/securepower-screenshot.png" alt="SecurePower Android anti-theft app by Gokul K — Kotlin and Firebase security app" width="800" height="450" loading="lazy" />
```

